  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>ASP.NET page contains DropDownList with items representing Visual WebGui&nbsp;<em>Form </em>names to be showed inside <em>FormBox </em>control. Change DropDownList's&nbsp;selected item to change the <em>Form </em>being<em>&nbsp;</em>shown in the FormBox.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>Visual WebGui&nbsp;<em>FormBox </em>control contains <em>Form </em>property to set the name of VWG&nbsp;Form<em> </em>to load.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>